subject: Wrestling
Mixed Martial Arts
lead_paragraph: T.J. Dillashaw and Dominick Cruz, who like so many M.M.A. stars got their start in amateur wrestling, will fight for Dillashaw’s bantamweight title on Sunday in Boston.
